Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:33.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:37.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Simoun from the {\i1}Arcus Niger{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:39.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Minister!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:41.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,What.. what is this?\N What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:44.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Arcus Niger{\i0}…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:46.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,…has gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:48.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:51.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seven o’clock high!\N Five ancient Simoun, closing in fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:53.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:07.73,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Sortie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.33,0:02:10.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Four o’clock level! \NAircraft silhouettes sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Confirm that, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:15.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,They appear to be \NArgentine cruise missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:17.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vyura, you take a Simile.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:20.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should we…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard the enemy \NSimoun are here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:26.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’ll destroy the missiles\N headed for the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:28.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,And the Highlands’ Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} and the {\i1}Messis{\i0}…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:32.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,…will have to deal with \Nthem on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:33.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:34.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:38.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right now, we need to do\N what we can, with all our might!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:54.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Falcon Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:55.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Falcon Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:57.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Falcon Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nine o’clock low!\N More aeroplane silhouettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Identify them! How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Argentine cruise missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Number: twenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:15.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rodoreamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:18.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Three o’clock low, \Nmore missiles incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:19.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:22.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it’s nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:30.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Whether we perform Ri Maajons to send off\N the souls of the dead, or to drive away the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,it doesn’t change the fact that we’re performing Ri Maajons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,At least, that’s what I {\i1}used{\i0} to think…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:39.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:10.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Para-sama!\N— Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, the shrapnel\N is going to fall on the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:23.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:39.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,…but I don’t believe that any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:42.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ri Maajons are the same,\Nbut their meaning is totally different!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you two all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas, she…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:08.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:11.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rodoreamon, how about you? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:14.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:17.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta, what about\N the enemy Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:20.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually… I’m not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,They seem to have run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:23.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’re turning around\N and flying away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:27.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you certain of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:31.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,The enemy’s Highland Simoun \Nwill soon be out of visual range, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:37.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why didn’t the enemy Simoun attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:42.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they had attacked us…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:44.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,…we would have been wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:52.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Guragief.\N— Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your quarters, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:11.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Defence Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf, what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:23.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simile which was carrying\N Sibylla Mamiina’s body…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:24.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,…has not returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:29.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was almost certainly\N intercepted by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:33.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,It goes without saying, but the incident took place within our Holy Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:36.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,We no longer have control \Nof our own airspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:38.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:39.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,What of Sibylla Mamiina’s body?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:47.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief, we have no time for such trivial matters. The situation is already—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you just say that Sibylla Mamiina’s body is a trivial matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:53.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Minister, did I really \Njust hear you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:54.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:57.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are not to inform\N the sibyllae of this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:00.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:04.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,The appearance of the Simoun among the Argentine forces today…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:10.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,…was a show of force, to prove to us that they can attack whenever they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:14.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that really is what\N they’re capable of doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:34.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can’t believe that this could have happened while we were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:37.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,There has to be something \Nwe can do to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:51.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:55.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,How is your wound,\N Sibylla Morinas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wapourif!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:08:00.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wapourif, do you know \Nhow to wrap a bandage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:05.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, Rodoreamon’s lack of skill is shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, allow me, Sibylla Rodoreamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,The flight surgeon was busy, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:16.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,The doc’s at the Grand Temple, tending to the people who were hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:17.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:20.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I’ll leave her in your\N capable hands, Wapourif!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:22.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma’am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:24.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:30.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are still a lot of things that we’ll have to do, aren’t there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:37.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,But… I like the Ri Maajons that we offer to Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:42.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,And you know, I think \Neveryone else feels the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:43.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,How’s the damage to the Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I believe that we will only\N need to replace the canopy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:06.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, we just finished repairing the Sibylla Aurea’s Simoun, and now this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was there no other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:12.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah… it was the only thing we could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:16.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you please take\N better care of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:19.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will ask you once more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:51.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do we really have no way to repel the combined forces of the Highlands and the Archipelago?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,At such a critical time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:10:01.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you{\i0} were the one responsible for carrying off three of our Simoun sibyllae!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:05.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think that we are well past \Nthe time for recriminations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:09.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, let us return to \Nthe object of this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,One hour ago, \Nthe Highlands and Archipelago
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:18.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,proposed a ceasefire between their alliance and our Simulacrum Theocracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:24.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,To think they are suing for peace,\Nwhen they have the power to defeat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:28.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hope you haven’t forgotten the Highlanders’ previous method of “negotiating” a peace agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:32.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, but the people are voicing their desire for an end to this war!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can’t you see that these “proposals” of theirs are just lies?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.74,0:10:36.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not again…\N\h
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:39.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we had opened peace talks earlier, we would have—
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.57,0:10:41.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}sick{\i0} of hearing about your grudges against us.\N\h
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:49.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can’t do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:51.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s not true, Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:56.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter how you think of yourself,\N you are a Simoun sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:11:00.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t know about \Nanything but fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.23,0:11:02.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t know how to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:06.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,…she was a fighter, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:14.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,But her prayers \Nblessed many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:17.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,The people looked to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,The priestesses will\N protect us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:26.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,The priestesses will \Ndefeat all the bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:29.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s right… so you must\N be patient, little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:30.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's a good child.
Comment: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry. I didn’t think\N you would be here…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:55.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:12:00.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril and Aaeru are \Nblessing the people below.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:02.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:04.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,To think that Aaeru’s participating, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:06.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:09.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I would have expected you \Nto be the first to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. That’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:24.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamiina…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:28.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think she belongs\N by your side, Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t really understand why,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,but I feel that you\N should have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:51.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:57.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun, would you take care of Mamiina for me from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:00.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:14.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I never thought that you would keep something secret from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:17.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neither did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:23.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just don’t understand\N what you want any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:28.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I want, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:40.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guys, it’s an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:44.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:51.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril! It seems that they’re pushing for another peace treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:54.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I heard about it from Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is this information reliable?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sibylla Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:00.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:02.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Were you the one who told her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Only a handful of people know of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:08.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I decided that you deserved to be told.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:10.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:13.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Will the war really end this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:15.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:21.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Angulas came to us pretending to be a translator for the peace conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:24.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but… maybe this time it’s for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:29.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is possible that you will all be able to leave the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:36.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever. There’s nothing we can really do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:38.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, you’re right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:41.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can only do… what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:48.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief, about our operational plan…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:51.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:52.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:55.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,A little while ago,\N Paraietta said the very same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:58.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,…and we’ll help with that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:59.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:01.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,To guard against incursions \Nfrom the mountain sector,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:03.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’d like to send out rotating patrols.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,I understand we’re in \Nthe middle of a crisis, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} is so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:18.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:21.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,To think that the {\i1}Arcus Niger{\i0}, a ship of the same class, has gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s shocking. Almost unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:25.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:31.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s almost as hard to believe as you and Guragief fighting with each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:33.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re aware of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:39.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,You both have strong feelings… that you’re unwilling to concede.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief is… too earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:47.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, he sure can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s a shame that you \Nboth decided to be men.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:52.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,You should patch things up with Guragief as quickly as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:58.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,You never know when\N your time will be up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:15:59.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have to get back to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:05.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:08.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Kaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:12.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why are they attacking us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:15.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like they say, “they won’t quit\N until we make them.”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:23.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Cast off the moonrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Casting off the moonrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:31.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Up ship! Climb at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ascending at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Situation report!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:47.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Seven o’clock high! \NFive ancient Simoun approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:52.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Eleven o’clock level, \Nseveral Argentine medium fighters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ready the Simoun for immediate takeoff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:56.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:04.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where are the priestesses\N from Chor Tempest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:05.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’re not here yet, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:06.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:09.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for, Anubituf?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:11.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Order Chor Tempest to sortie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,The enemy is almost upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:13.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.73,0:17:14.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:17.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:26.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Send word for the sibyllae to stand by on the port flight deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ll give their orders to them in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:29.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:32.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief, I need to ask you \Nto take over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:36.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0} will be \Nthe second wave of our attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:37.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ll leave you to direct \Nour offensive from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:43.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Until the Captain returns,\N I have the conn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:44.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:47.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are they doing? Go! Fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:51.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our orders are to stand by\N on the port flight deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:52.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:57.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Damn that Anubituf! \NWhat is that sly bastard plotting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:59.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Standing by at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:17:59.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,That geezer is so freakin’ annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:02.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you wait, Sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:08.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:11.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:16.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even though it may not look like it,\NI used to be a sibylla, just like all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then you’re going to fly a Simile?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:23.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. We have only five Simoun with which to intercept the enemy attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:28.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,I shall fly a Simile, and issue orders directly to you all from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:29.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,I will need you to follow those orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:30.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:31.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:37.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Morinas, how is your wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:41.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s been very carefully treated. \NEverything is fine, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:45.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,— G-Get a Simile ready, now!\N— Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:07.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae, a word if you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:12.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have dragged you into this war… and that must come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:17.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,I very much regret that \Nwe have not been able to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:20.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Captain Anubituf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:23.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens,\N I shall never forget your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:25.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nah, you guys don’t need to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:27.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,We already decided, didn’t we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:28.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,What we can do now…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:31.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,…we will do with all our might!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:39.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are drastically outnumbered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:43.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,We shall pull them towards us as much as we can, dive rapidly, and then hit them hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:49.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,The course of the battle will be decided by this first attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:57.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:40.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,All batteries, fire at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:03.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’re running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:04.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go to hell, suckers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:06.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:10.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,We showed those losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:14.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,The two of you, watch your mouths!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:16.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Y-You heard us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:19.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course not! We were \Njust talking about you two,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:21.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,and figured that you were probably saying something filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:24.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good work, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:29.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey! What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:30.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, do tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:33.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Probably another inane \Ncomment from Floe, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:36.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that’s likely, \Nisn’t it, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.43,0:21:37.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:40.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn’t say anything like that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:42.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is Chor Tempest always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:41.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Alti’s the one who always—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:43.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? Floe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:43.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:54.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Captain’s Simile, approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.32,0:21:56.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,All hands, salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:21.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Despite Chor Tempest’s actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:25.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Central Command concluded that the war was a lost cause…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:33.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,…and accepted the peace treaty offered by Plumbum and Argentum a few days later.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:06.67,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:10.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,As Alliance soldiers take control\N of the {\i1}Arcus Prima{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.51,0:24:13.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest is disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:15.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Simoun:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.43,0:24:18.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Eternal Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.55,0:24:20.02,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}The Eternal Maiden
